N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 122.5 - Disposition of complaint

State Regulations
(a) All complaints (Part I) forwarded to the

Albany office of the Department of Motor Vehicles will be maintained in the
department's files for at least four months after disposition of the
charge. (b) Part I of each issued
ticket which is not properly returnable before the bureau will be delivered to
the appropriate court or tribunal. Notes
